This is a blog for Django projects

Requirements:
    django-tiny_mce
    a version of filebrowser

Principal Ideas behind this blog:
  * Takes basic-aps' blog a little closer to Wordpress, without overbloat
  * Easy installation ( installs with TinyMce and filebrowser already configured
  * Very little or no logic in templates
  
Idea Brainstorm:
  * livesettings
  
